{"tid":1072951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜車隊突現身西環 韓國瑜落車後不發一言進入中聯辦","createTime":"2019-03-22T10:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T12:54:15.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f40a6b481870abdf45565c99de70cbfda3c37fc","tid":1072951,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/309342/韓國瑜訪港-韓國瑜入中聯辦料晤王志民\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F309342%2F%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%A8%AA%E6%B8%AF-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%96%99%E6%99%A4%E7%8E%8B%E5%BF%97%E6%B0%91&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=36d154f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/309342/韓國瑜訪港-韓國瑜入中聯辦料晤王志民</a><br />\n<br />\n正在香港訪問的高雄市長韓國瑜上午與特首林鄭月娥會面後，下午出席在會展舉行的高雄市經貿簡介會，及至下午5時半左右，車隊令人意外地現身西環，韓國瑜落車後不發一言，徑自進入中聯辦。<br />\n<br />\n媒體記者未允許跟隨進入採訪，但預料韓國瑜會與中聯辦主任王志民見面。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜下午出席在會展舉行的高雄市經貿簡介會，指高雄的漁農業界在會上簽署七項合同，總值近23億元新台幣。他對香港入口的農產品當中台灣只佔3.6%感到震撼，認為台灣過去忽略香港市場，未來希望可以將佔比升至一成，認為是合理及可以達到的目標，又希望高雄香港兩地一家親。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜無回答有關一國兩制、九二共識及會否參加總統選舉等問題，強調今次是經濟及情感交流之旅，又指無法比較今次訪問的規格，只感到非常熱情，氣氛非常融洽。"},{"pid":"636cb38b87f5b0ae23042c6154aa839d3235e724","tid":1072951,"uid":87780,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:53:50.000Z","msg":"做咗三個月咁快去中聯辦述職?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa8e415e91a094be947fd17b7dfa34ab705bcd3","tid":1072951,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔改姓做中國瑜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48afbc4c62d5e65b58a7115217e78363c603209a","tid":1072951,"uid":52090,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/unphNOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FunphNOf.jpg&h=595f403e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VOuOFSr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVOuOFSr.jpg&h=1064ac49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RZWKRhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRZWKRhv.jpg&h=e2587119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XUnCFDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXUnCFDM.jpg&h=b67b8c69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7efc416488f0961aa1309bbd70ca38bbe01ade77","tid":1072951,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"根本通番賣國, 你話黎同香港傾生意都講唔通啦, 應該好似果條大除婆咁, 吊銷佢台籍就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7403357f31354be3491cb76bbbed30bc8fc1efa8","tid":1072951,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"copy 錯左第一張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf72ed7051b561c636b3eeab2c27cfb3ee409484","tid":1072951,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"明修棧道 暗渡陳倉<br />\n扮訪港原來真正原來係為左呢樣嘢"}]}